<p>fine little place with all sorts of shops &amp; trams in her.   There are some very fine buildings including a splendid Cathedral.   The tower shows traces of the fighting which seems to have taken place in &amp; around her at the beginning of the war.   There are five big hot baths here for the troops, &amp; a big building is set apart for the soldiers &amp; it has all conveniences such as restaurants, reading &amp; writing rooms, pianos &amp; such like handy things.</p>
